name: Landwolf
description: First Landwolf on the Ethereum blockchain. Landwolf, a charismatic and carefree wolf character from Matt Furie’s “Boy’s Club” comic series, is known for his laid-back attitude, affinity for fun, and the iconic catchphrase “Feels good man.” As a friend of the internet sensation Pepe the Frog, Landwolf shares in the adventures and humor that have endeared the comic characters to fans worldwide. Together with Pepe and their other friends, Landwolf navigates the absurdity of life, leaving a trail of moments and laughter in his wake.
